libchdr
------------------------------------------
Standalone library for reading MAME's CHDv1-v5 formats

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.2.0-1
  libchdr-devel-0.1+git20211003-1bl1
  libchdr0.1-0.1+git20211003-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1
  zlib0-1.2.11-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.37-2
  cmake-3.20.0-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  ninja-1.10.2-1
  zlib-devel-1.2.11-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/rtissera/libchdr

Canonical download:
  git://github.com/rtissera/libchdr.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libchdr-0.1+git20211003-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libchdr-0.1+git20211003-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libchdr-0.1+git20211003-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libchdr-0.1+git20211003-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libchdr0.1-0.1+git20211003-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libchdr-devel-0.1+git20211003-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libchdr)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libchdr.README
  /usr/share/doc/libchdr/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/libchdr/README.md

(libchdr0.1)
  /usr/bin/cygchdr-0.1.dll

(libchdr-devel)
  /usr/include/libchdr/bitstream.h
  /usr/include/libchdr/cdrom.h
  /usr/include/libchdr/chd.h
  /usr/include/libchdr/chdconfig.h
  /usr/include/libchdr/coretypes.h
  /usr/include/libchdr/flac.h
  /usr/include/libchdr/huffman.h
  /usr/lib/libchdr.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libchdr.pc

